             was indicted for <rs id="t17870221-15-off81" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17870221-15-off81" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17870221-15-off81" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17870221-15-cd82" type="crimeDate">21st of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17870221-15-off81 t17870221-15-cd82"></join>, one piece of cotton check for aprons, containing forty-three yards, value 39 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17870221-15-victim204" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Rimer
                  <interp inst="t17870221-15-victim204" type="surname" value="Rimer"></interp>
